<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Upwinxp-20241123171600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu-20241123171600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Wikipedija v ePravopisu&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Wikipedija v ePravopisu&quot;}--><h2 id="Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu" data-mw-thread-id="h-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu-20241123171600"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu-20241123171600"/>Wikipedija v ePravopisu<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu-20241123171600"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=1" title="Uredi razdelek: Wikipedija v ePravopisu" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Wikipedija v ePravopisu"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Upwinxp-20241123171600","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu-20241123171600","replies":["c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-\u017diga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600","timestamp":"20250104155900"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__14__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__8__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Upwinxp-20241123171600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu-20241123171600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Wikipedija v ePravopisu&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Wikipedija v ePravopisu&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu"/>Slučajno sem opazil, da so v nastajajoči <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://fran.si/iskanje?View=1&amp;Query=wiki*">ePravopis</a> vključena gesla <i>Wikipedija</i> (lastno ime), <i>Wikipedijin</i> in <i>wikipedist/-ka</i>. Čestitke <span typeof="mw:File"><span><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/Emoji_Grinning_Face_Smiling_Eyes.svg/20px-Emoji_Grinning_Face_Smiling_Eyes.svg.png" decoding="async" width="18" height="18" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/Emoji_Grinning_Face_Smiling_Eyes.svg/40px-Emoji_Grinning_Face_Smiling_Eyes.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="128" data-file-height="128"/></span></span> —<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Upwinxp" title="Uporabnik:Upwinxp">Upwinxp</a> <a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Upwinxp" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Upwinxp">✉</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">18:16, 23. november 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="e&#10;xt-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241123171600","author":"Upwinxp","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu","replies":["c-A09-20241123203500-Upwinxp-20241123171600","c-GeographieMan-20241124110600-Upwinxp-20241123171600","c-Pinky_sl-20241124153600-Upwinxp-20241123171600","c-\u017diga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Upwinxp-20241123171600-Wikipedija_v_ePravopisu"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://giphy.com/gifs/yJFeycRK2DB4c"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-A09-20241123203500-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/>Lepo!</a> <b><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:A09" title="Uporabnik:A09"><span style="color:#004d99">A09</span></a></b>|<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:A09" title="Uporabniški pogovor:A09"><span style="color:#004d99">(pogovor)</span></a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-A09-20241123203500-Upwinxp-20241123171600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">21:35, 23. november 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-A09-20241123203500-Upwinxp-20241123171600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241123203500","author":"A09","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-A09-20241123203500-Upwinxp-20241123171600","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-A09-20241123203500-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/></dd>
<dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-GeographieMan-20241124110600-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/>Super! :D — <i><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:GeographieMan" title="Uporabnik:GeographieMan"><b><span style="color: #4863A0;">GeographieMan</span></b></a></i><sup>[<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:GeographieMan" title="Uporabniški pogovor:GeographieMan"><b>~MSG~</b></a>]</sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-GeographieMan-20241124110600-Upwinxp-20241123171600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:06, 24. november 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-GeographieMan-20241124110600-Upwinxp-20241123171600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241124110600","author":"GeographieMan","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-GeographieMan-20241124110600-Upwinxp-20241123171600","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-GeographieMan-20241124110600-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/></dd>
<dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Pinky_sl-20241124153600-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/><span class="Emoji noviewer"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/Slika:Emojione_1F60D.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img alt="😍" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f5/Emojione_1F60D.svg/20px-Emojione_1F60D.svg.png" decoding="async" width="16" height="16" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f5/Emojione_1F60D.svg/40px-Emojione_1F60D.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512"/></a></span></span> --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Pinky_sl" title="Uporabnik:Pinky sl">Pinky sl</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Pinky_sl" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Pinky sl">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Pinky_sl-20241124153600-Upwinxp-20241123171600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">16:36, 24. november 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Pinky_sl-20241124153600-Upwinxp-20241123171600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241124153600","author":"Pinky sl","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Pinky_sl-20241124153600-Upwinxp-20241123171600","replies":["c-TadejM-20241124233800-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","c-TadejM-20241225091400-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","c-TadejM-20241226110100-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","c-TadejM-20241226233700-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Pinky_sl-20241124153600-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-TadejM-20241124233800-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>Me veseli, da so vključili. To je uveljavljena oblika. Sicer želim opozoriti, da se v angleščini uporablja zapis <i>Wikipedians</i> in ne npr. <i>Wikipedists</i>.<a class="external autonumber" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Wikipedians#Nomenclature">[1]</a> Tako je vključeno tudi v Oxfordov slovar. To poudarja pripadnost skupnosti. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:TadejM" title="Uporabnik:TadejM">TadejM</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:TadejM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:TadejM">pogovor</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-TadejM-20241124233800-Pinky_sl-20241124153600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">00:38, 25. november 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-TadejM-20241124233800-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241124233800","author":"TadejM","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-TadejM-20241124233800-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","replies":["c-Yerpo-20241125054600-TadejM-20241124233800"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-TadejM-20241124233800-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Yerpo-20241125054600-TadejM-20241124233800"/>Verjetno se jim je zdelo bolj smotrno poudariti analogijo z besedo "enciklopedist". Ko bomo veliki, pa bo v slovarju tudi beseda wikimedijec. — <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Yerpo" title="Uporabnik:Yerpo">Yerpo</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Yerpo" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Yerpo">Ha?</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Yerpo-20241125054600-TadejM-20241124233800" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">06:46, 25. november 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Yerpo-20241125054600-TadejM-20241124233800"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241125054600","author":"Yerpo","type":"comment","level":4,"id":"c-Yerpo-20241125054600-TadejM-20241124233800","replies":["c-XJaM-20241225090700-Yerpo-20241125054600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Yerpo-20241125054600-TadejM-20241124233800"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-XJaM-20241225090700-Yerpo-20241125054600"/>Lepo. Poudarja tudi pripadnost občestvu. Makedonsko govoreči, če ste opazili, so na primer, preden so postali wikimedijci, imeli dve registrirani predstavnici svojega občestva. Vira sta nekje na njihovih straneh. Mi smo trenutno, kaj že, uporabniki skupine / user group. Ali sta potem, kot je omenil <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:TadejM" title="Uporabnik:TadejM">Tadej</a>, v igri lahko tudi obliki »wikipedijanec / wikipedijanka«? Ima malo čuden prizvok, tudi v Oxfordovem angleškem slovarju očitno, saj spominja na obliko Ind*ian. Znana jamajška pesem poje nekako takole: »The Arawaks were there first, ...« Kakšne indijanke neki. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:XJaM" title="Uporabnik:XJaM">XJaM</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:XJaM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:XJaM">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-XJaM-20241225090700-Yerpo-20241125054600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:07, 25. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-XJaM-20241225090700-Yerpo-20241125054600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241225090700","author":"XJaM","type":"comment","level":5,"id":"c-XJaM-20241225090700-Yerpo-20241125054600","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-XJaM-20241225090700-Yerpo-20241125054600"/></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-TadejM-20241225091400-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>Če bi želeli slediti angleškemu zgledu, bi bolj naravno zvenela oblika <i>wikipedijec</i>/<i>wikipedijka</i>. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:TadejM" title="Uporabnik:TadejM">TadejM</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:TadejM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:TadejM">pogovor</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-TadejM-20241225091400-Pinky_sl-20241124153600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:14, 25. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-TadejM-20241225091400-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241225091400","author":"TadejM","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-TadejM-20241225091400-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","replies":["c-XJaM-20241225171400-TadejM-20241225091400","c-Upwinxp-20241226102500-TadejM-20241225091400"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-TadejM-20241225091400-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-XJaM-20241225171400-TadejM-20241225091400"/>Aha. Ta oblika pa zveni kot In*dijka / In*dijec, kar sicer pmsm ni nič narobe. Kaj pa wikipedec / wikipedka. Zveni kot vsev*edec / vsev*edka, kar mnogi mislijo, da tudi so. Kot ni wikipedija slovar, tudi wikipedijec (wikipedec) ni vsevedec. Slišali pa bomo gotovo še marsikaj. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:XJaM" title="Uporabnik:XJaM">XJaM</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:XJaM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:XJaM">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-XJaM-20241225171400-TadejM-20241225091400" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">18:14, 25. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-XJaM-20241225171400-TadejM-20241225091400"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241225171400","author":"XJaM","type":"comment","level":5,"id":"c-XJaM-20241225171400-TadejM-20241225091400","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-XJaM-20241225171400-TadejM-20241225091400"/></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><dl><dd><dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Upwinxp-20241226102500-TadejM-20241225091400"/>Hm, zakaj pa bi se morali ozirati na angleški ali katerikoli zgled? —<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Upwinxp" title="Uporabnik:Upwinxp">Upwinxp</a> <a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Upwinxp" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Upwinxp">✉</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Upwinxp-20241226102500-TadejM-20241225091400" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">11:25, 26. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Upwinxp-20241226102500-TadejM-20241225091400"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241226102500","author":"Upwinxp","type":"comment","level":5,"id":"c-Upwinxp-20241226102500-TadejM-20241225091400","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Upwinxp-20241226102500-TadejM-20241225091400"/></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-TadejM-20241226110100-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>Nisem napisal, da bi se morali. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:TadejM" title="Uporabnik:TadejM">TadejM</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:TadejM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:TadejM">pogovor</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-TadejM-20241226110100-Pinky_sl-20241124153600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:01, 26. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-TadejM-20241226110100-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241226110100","author":"TadejM","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-TadejM-20241226110100-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","replies":["c-Upwinxp-20241226180600-TadejM-20241226110100"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-TadejM-20241226110100-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Upwinxp-20241226180600-TadejM-20241226110100"/>No, no, pa čemu bi se morda želeli. —<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Upwinxp" title="Uporabnik:Upwinxp">Upwinxp</a> <a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Upwinxp" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Upwinxp">✉</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Upwinxp-20241226180600-TadejM-20241226110100" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">19:06, 26. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Upwinxp-20241226180600-TadejM-20241226110100"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241226180600","author":"Upwinxp","type":"comment","level":4,"id":"c-Upwinxp-20241226180600-TadejM-20241226110100","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Upwinxp-20241226180600-TadejM-20241226110100"/></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-TadejM-20241226233700-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/>Kot rečeno, poudarja pripadnost skupnosti. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:TadejM" title="Uporabnik:TadejM">TadejM</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:TadejM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:TadejM">pogovor</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-TadejM-20241226233700-Pinky_sl-20241124153600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">00:37, 27. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-TadejM-20241226233700-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-rep&#10;lylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241226233700","author":"TadejM","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-TadejM-20241226233700-Pinky_sl-20241124153600","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-TadejM-20241226233700-Pinky_sl-20241124153600"/></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://fran.si/iskanje?View=1&amp;Query=lajkati"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Žiga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/>Lajkamo</a> :) <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:%C5%BDiga" title="Uporabnik:Žiga">Žiga</a> <a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:%C5%BDiga" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Žiga">✉</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Žiga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">16:59, 4. januar 2025 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Žiga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250104155900","author":"\u017diga","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-\u017diga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Žiga-20250104155900-Upwinxp-20241123171600"/></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-XJaM-20241225091200&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-2025-20241225091200&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025&quot;,&quot;h-Lansko_leto_v_\u0161tevilkah-2025-20250101100900&quot;,&quot;h-Najbolj_obiskane_strani-2025-20250101110200&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;2025&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;2025&quot;}--><h2 id="2025" data-mw-thread-id="h-2025-20241225091200"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-2025-20241225091200"/>2025<span data-mw-comment-end="h-2025-20241225091200"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2" title="Uredi razdelek: 2025" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: 2025"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-XJaM-20241225091200","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-2025-20241225091200","replies":["c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025","h-Lansko_leto_v_\u0161tevilkah-2025-20250101100900","h-Najbolj_obiskane_strani-2025-20250101110200"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Pinky_sl-20250104174800-Yerpo-20250101100900","timestamp":"20250104174800"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__9__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__6__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-XJaM-20241225091200&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-2025-20241225091200&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025&quot;,&quot;h-Lansko_leto_v_\u0161tevilkah-2025-20250101100900&quot;,&quot;h-Najbolj_obiskane_strani-2025-20250101110200&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;2025&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;2025&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025"/>Da ne bo <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Yerpo" title="Uporabnik:Yerpo">Jernej</a> spet prvi kot lani, želim vsem uporabnikom slovenske wikipedije in sestrskih projektov, še posebej aktivnim, v novem letu 2025 veliko sreče in  še več zdravja. <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:XJaM" title="Uporabnik:XJaM">XJaM</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:XJaM" title="Uporabniški pogovor:XJaM">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:12, 25. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241225091200","author":"XJaM","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025","replies":["c-Yerpo-20241226104300-XJaM-20241225091200"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-XJaM-20241225091200-2025"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Yerpo-20241226104300-XJaM-20241225091200"/>Si se pa res potrudil biti prvi ^.^ Od mene zaenkrat lepe praznike vsem, pregled sledi, kot običajno, takoj po novem letu. — <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Yerpo" title="Uporabnik:Yerpo">Yerpo</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Yerpo" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Yerpo">Ha?</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Yerpo-20241226104300-XJaM-20241225091200" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">11:43, 26. december 2024 (CET)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Yerpo-20241226104300-XJaM-20241225091200"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20241226104300","author":"Yerpo","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Yerpo-20241226104300-XJaM-20241225091200","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Yerpo-20241226104300-XJaM-20241225091200"/></dd></dl>
<p><br/>
Srečno in zdravo 2025 torej, pa veliko navdiha za delo vsem želim <span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/Slika:Smile_smile.png" class="mw-file-description" title=":-)"><img alt=":-)" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4b/Smile_smile.png" decoding="async" width="12" height="12" class="mw-file-element" data-file-width="12" data-file-height="12"/></a></span>. Kot obljubljeno:
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Lansko_leto_v_številkah" data-mw-thread-id="h-Lansko_leto_v_številkah-2025-20250101100900"><span id="Lansko_leto_v_.C5.A1tevilkah"/><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Lansko_leto_v_številkah-2025-20250101100900"/>Lansko leto v številkah<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Lansko_leto_v_številkah-2025-20250101100900"/></h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=3" title="Uredi razdelek: Lansko leto v številkah" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Lansko leto v številkah"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
