<p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://1ka.arnes.si/slovenscina2025"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200-Slovenščina_danes:_anketa_o_potrebah_jezikovnih_uporabnikov_v_Republiki_Sloven"/>Slovinčina dnes: prieskum o potrebách používateľov jazykov v Slovinskej republike</a> <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Du%C5%A1an_Krehe%C4%BE" title="Uporabnik:Dušan Kreheľ">Dušan Kreheľ</a> (<a href="/w/index.php?title=Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Du%C5%A1an_Krehe%C4%BE&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Dušan Kreheľ (stran ne obstaja)">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200-Slovenščina_danes:_anketa_o_potrebah_jezikovnih_uporabnikov_v_Republiki_Sloven" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:02, 31. marec 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200-Slovenščina_danes:_anketa_o_potrebah_jezikovnih_uporabnikov_v_Republiki_Sloven"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250331100200","author":"Du\u0161an Krehe\u013e","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250331100200-Sloven\u0161\u010dina_danes:_anketa_o_potrebah_jezikovnih_uporabnikov_v_Republiki_Sloven","replies":["c-Smihael-20250331122100-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250331100200"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200-Slovenščina_danes:_anketa_o_potrebah_jezikovnih_uporabnikov_v_Republiki_Sloven"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Smihael-20250331122100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200"/>Hvala za deljenje povezave. Mislim, da je anketa relavantna tudi za soustvarjalce Wikipedije. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Smihael" title="Uporabnik:Smihael">Miha</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Smihael-20250331122100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">14:21, 31. marec 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Smihael-20250331122100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250331122100","author":"Smihael","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Smihael-20250331122100-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250331100200","replies":[],"displayName":"Miha"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Smihael-20250331122100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250331100200"/></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-A09-20250401162400&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Predlogi_za_brisanje-20250401162400&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Predlogi za brisanje&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Predlogi za brisanje&quot;}--><h2 id="Predlogi_za_brisanje" data-mw-thread-id="h-Predlogi_za_brisanje-20250401162400"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Predlogi_za_brisanje-20250401162400"/>Predlogi za brisanje<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Predlogi_za_brisanje-20250401162400"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=27" title="Uredi razdelek: Predlogi za brisanje" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Predlogi za brisanje"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-A09-20250401162400","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Predlogi_za_brisanje-20250401162400","replies":["c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje","timestamp":"20250401162400"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-A09-20250401162400&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Predlogi_za_brisanje-20250401162400&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Predlogi za brisanje&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Predlogi za brisanje&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje"/>Prosim skupnost, če malo pokomentira trenutne predloge za brisanje, da lahko kakšnega tudi zapremo. Enega izmed adminov bi tudi prosil, če jih zapre (da ne bom jaz imel konflikta interesov). Ob tej priliki vabim tudi h komentiranju <a href="/wiki/Wikipedija:Predlogi_za_brisanje/Glavna_stran" title="Wikipedija:Predlogi za brisanje/Glavna stran">Wikipedija:Predlogi za brisanje/Glavna stran</a>. LP, <b><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:A09" title="Uporabnik:A09"><span style="color:#82201F; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">A09</span></a></b>|<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:A09" title="Uporabniški pogovor:A09"><span style="color:#797976; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">(pogovor)</span></a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">18:24, 1. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250401162400","author":"A09","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-A09-20250401162400-Predlogi_za_brisanje"/>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Blueginger2-20250412101200&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-SFN-20250412101200&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;SFN&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;SFN&quot;}--><h2 id="SFN" data-mw-thread-id="h-SFN-20250412101200"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-SFN-20250412101200"/>SFN<span data-mw-comment-end="h-SFN-20250412101200"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=28" title="Uredi razdelek: SFN" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=28" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: SFN"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Blueginger2-20250412101200","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-SFN-20250412101200","replies":["c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600","timestamp":"20250412111100"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__5__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Blueginger2-20250412101200&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-SFN-20250412101200&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;SFN&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;SFN&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN"/>Mi lahko kdo pomaga s "sfn" citati med besedilom v mojem članku <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Blueginger2/peskovnik3" title="Uporabnik:Blueginger2/peskovnik3">Uporabnik:Blueginger2/peskovnik3</a>. Med sklici na koncu besedila se ne izpiše nič. Hvala. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Blueginger2" title="Uporabnik:Blueginger2">Blueginger2</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Blueginger2" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Blueginger2">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:12, 12. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250412101200","author":"Blueginger2","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN","replies":["c-A09-20250412105200-Blueginger2-20250412101200"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Blueginger2-20250412101200-SFN"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-A09-20250412105200-Blueginger2-20250412101200"/><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="Da" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Yes_check.svg/20px-Yes_check.svg.png" decoding="async" width="18" height="18" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Yes_check.svg/40px-Yes_check.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600"/></span></span><span style="display:none">D</span> <b>Opravljeno</b> Ne vem sicer če ti je slučajno kako kopiranje tole povzročilo, ampak {{<a href="/wiki/Predloga:Sfn" title="Predloga:Sfn">sfn</a>}} ne uporablja ref značk. Popravljeno. LP, <b><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:A09" title="Uporabnik:A09"><span style="color:#82201F; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">A09</span></a></b>|<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:A09" title="Uporabniški pogovor:A09"><span style="color:#797976; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">(pogovor)</span></a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-A09-20250412105200-Blueginger2-20250412101200" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:52, 12. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-A09-20250412105200-Blueginger2-20250412101200"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250412105200","author":"A09","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-A09-20250412105200-Blueginger2-20250412101200","replies":["c-Blueginger2-20250412105700-A09-20250412105200"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-A09-20250412105200-Blueginger2-20250412101200"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Blueginger2-20250412105700-A09-20250412105200"/>Najlepša hvala! Tisti ref so bili del "Opcit" citatov na madžarski Wikipediji, npr.: <sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>1<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Blueginger2" title="Uporabnik:Blueginger2">Blueginger2</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Blueginger2" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Blueginger2">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Blueginger2-20250412105700-A09-20250412105200" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:57, 12. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discus&#10;siontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Blueginger2-20250412105700-A09-20250412105200"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250412105700","author":"Blueginger2","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-Blueginger2-20250412105700-A09-20250412105200","replies":["c-A09-20250412110600-Blueginger2-20250412105700"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Blueginger2-20250412105700-A09-20250412105200"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-A09-20250412110600-Blueginger2-20250412105700"/>Mnja, bi bilo pametno narediti en parser, podoben tistim za reference z nemške wiki. <b><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:A09" title="Uporabnik:A09"><span style="color:#82201F; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">A09</span></a></b>|<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:A09" title="Uporabniški pogovor:A09"><span style="color:#797976; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">(pogovor)</span></a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-A09-20250412110600-Blueginger2-20250412105700" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">13:06, 12. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-A09-20250412110600-Blueginger2-20250412105700"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250412110600","author":"A09","type":"comment","level":4,"id":"c-A09-20250412110600-Blueginger2-20250412105700","replies":["c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-A09-20250412110600-Blueginger2-20250412105700"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600"/>Ja, mogoče bo še kdo kaj prevajal iz huwiki... --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Blueginger2" title="Uporabnik:Blueginger2">Blueginger2</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Blueginger2" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Blueginger2">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">13:11, 12. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250412111100","author":"Blueginger2","type":"comment","level":5,"id":"c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Blueginger2-20250412111100-A09-20250412110600"/></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
