<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Pinky_sl-20250429073000-dan_zelenja_(みどりの日)_na_Japonskem"/>Ali kdo ve kaj je to "dan zelenja (みどりの日) na Japonskem" na naši glavni strani (29. april - Na današnji dan). <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Pinky_sl" title="Uporabnik:Pinky sl">Pinky sl</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Pinky_sl" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Pinky sl">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Pinky_sl-20250429073000-dan_zelenja_(みどりの日)_na_Japonskem" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">09:30, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Pinky_sl-20250429073000-dan_zelenja_(みどりの日)_na_Japonskem"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429073000","author":"Pinky sl","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Pinky_sl-20250429073000-dan_zelenja_(\u307f\u3069\u308a\u306e\u65e5)_na_Japonskem","replies":["c-Yerpo-20250429073300-Pinky_sl-20250429073000"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Pinky_sl-20250429073000-dan_zelenja_(みどりの日)_na_Japonskem"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Yerpo-20250429073300-Pinky_sl-20250429073000"/>Najbrž <a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%81%BF%E3%81%A9%E3%82%8A%E3%81%AE%E6%97%A5" class="extiw" title="ja:みどりの日">ja:みどりの日</a> oziroma <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenery_Day" class="extiw" title="en:Greenery Day">en:Greenery Day</a>. Domnevam, da ni pomembnejših praznikov na ta dan in je avtor pogledal širše. — <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Yerpo" title="Uporabnik:Yerpo">Yerpo</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Yerpo" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Yerpo">Ha?</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Yerpo-20250429073300-Pinky_sl-20250429073000" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">09:33, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Yerpo-20250429073300-Pinky_sl-20250429073000"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429073300","author":"Yerpo","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Yerpo-20250429073300-Pinky_sl-20250429073000","replies":["c-Pinky_sl-20250429073700-Yerpo-20250429073300"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Yerpo-20250429073300-Pinky_sl-20250429073000"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Pinky_sl-20250429073700-Yerpo-20250429073300"/>Hvala, Yerpo. Me je zanimala tematika in sem iskala po slovenskih spletnih straneh, da bi kaj našla o tem in nisem bila zelo uspešna. --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Pinky_sl" title="Uporabnik:Pinky sl">Pinky sl</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Pinky_sl" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Pinky sl">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Pinky_sl-20250429073700-Yerpo-20250429073300" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">09:37, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Pinky_sl-20250429073700-Yerpo-20250429073300"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429073700","author":"Pinky sl","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-Pinky_sl-20250429073700-Yerpo-20250429073300","replies":["c-MZaplotnik-20250429081000-Pinky_sl-20250429073700"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Pinky_sl-20250429073700-Yerpo-20250429073300"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-MZaplotnik-20250429081000-Pinky_sl-20250429073700"/>Ampak danes je <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sh%C5%8Dwa_Day" class="extiw" title="en:Shōwa Day">Shōwa Day</a>, praznovanje <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenery_Day" class="extiw" title="en:Greenery Day">zelenja</a> so po več neskladjih prestavili na 4. maj. <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:MZaplotnik" title="Uporabnik:MZaplotnik"><span style="color:#9370DB;"><strong>MZa</strong></span><span style="color:#8B008B;">plot</span><span style="color:#191970;"><strong>nik</strong></span></a><sup><small>(<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:MZaplotnik" title="Uporabniški pogovor:MZaplotnik">sporočilo</a>)</small></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-MZaplotnik-20250429081000-Pinky_sl-20250429073700" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:10, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-MZaplotnik-20250429081000-Pinky_sl-20250429073700"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429081000","author":"MZaplotnik","type":"comment","level":4,"id":"c-MZaplotnik-20250429081000-Pinky_sl-20250429073700","replies":["c-Yerpo-20250429081600-MZaplotnik-20250429081000"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-MZaplotnik-20250429081000-Pinky_sl-20250429073700"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Yerpo-20250429081600-MZaplotnik-20250429081000"/>Viš, pa res, toliko nisem bil pozoren. Damo raje <a href="/w/index.php?title=Mednarodni_dan_plesa&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Mednarodni dan plesa (stran ne obstaja)">mednarodni dan plesa</a> ali nič kot nek obskuren japonski praznik? Sploh ne vem, kako bi prevedel njegov naziv brez izvirnega raziskovanja. — <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Yerpo" title="Uporabnik:Yerpo">Yerpo</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Yerpo" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Yerpo">Ha?</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Yerpo-20250429081600-MZaplotnik-20250429081000" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:16, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Yerpo-20250429081600-MZaplotnik-20250429081000"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429081600","author":"Yerpo","type":"comment","level":5,"id":"c-Yerpo-20250429081600-MZaplotnik-20250429081000","replies":["c-MZaplotnik-20250429082800-Yerpo-20250429081600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Yerpo-20250429081600-MZaplotnik-20250429081000"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-MZaplotnik-20250429082800-Yerpo-20250429081600"/>Ja sam za ples. Ker današnji japonski praznik je neprevedljiv in za njih zelo polarizajoč.  <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:MZaplotnik" title="Uporabnik:MZaplotnik"><span style="color:#9370DB;"><strong>MZa</strong></span><span style="color:#8B008B;">plot</span><span style="color:#191970;"><strong>nik</strong></span></a><sup><small>(<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:MZaplotnik" title="Uporabniški pogovor:MZaplotnik">sporočilo</a>)</small></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-MZaplotnik-20250429082800-Yerpo-20250429081600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:28, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-MZaplotnik-20250429082800-Yerpo-20250429081600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429082800","author":"MZaplotnik","type":"comment","level":6,"id":"c-MZaplotnik-20250429082800-Yerpo-20250429081600","replies":["c-Yerpo-20250429084800-MZaplotnik-20250429082800"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-MZaplotnik-20250429082800-Yerpo-20250429081600"/>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Yerpo-20250429084800-MZaplotnik-20250429082800"/><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="Da" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Yes_check.svg/20px-Yes_check.svg.png" decoding="async" width="18" height="18" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/Yes_check.svg/40px-Yes_check.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600"/></span></span><span style="display:none">D</span> <b>Ok</b> — <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Yerpo" title="Uporabnik:Yerpo">Yerpo</a> <sup><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Yerpo" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Yerpo">Ha?</a></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Yerpo-20250429084800-MZaplotnik-20250429082800" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">10:48, 29. april 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Yerpo-20250429084800-MZaplotnik-20250429082800"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250429084800","author":"Yerpo","type":"comment","level":7,"id":"c-Yerpo-20250429084800-MZaplotnik-20250429082800","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Yerpo-20250429084800-MZaplotnik-20250429082800"/></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!-20250506150800&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!&quot;}--><h2 id="We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!" data-mw-thread-id="h-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!-20250506150800"><span id="We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon.21"/><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!-20250506150800"/>We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!<span data-mw-comment-end="h-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!-20250506150800"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=35" title="Uredi razdelek: We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!-20250506150800","replies":["c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800","timestamp":"20250506185200"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!-20250506150800&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Sannita_(WMF)-202505
06150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;We will be enabling the new Charts extension on your wiki soon!&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><i><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!"/>(Apologies for posting in English)</i>
</p><p>Hi all! We have good news to share regarding the ongoing problem with graphs and charts affecting all wikis that use them.
</p><p>As you probably know, the <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Graph" class="extiw" title="mw:Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Graph">old Graph extension</a> was disabled in 2023 <a href="https://lists.wikimedia.org/hyperkitty/list/wikitech-l@lists.wikimedia.org/thread/EWL4AGBEZEDMNNFTM4FRD4MHOU3CVESO/" class="extiw" title="listarchive:list/wikitech-l@lists.wikimedia.org/thread/EWL4AGBEZEDMNNFTM4FRD4MHOU3CVESO/">due to security reasons</a>. We’ve worked in these two years to find a solution that could replace the old extension, and provide a safer and better solution to users who wanted to showcase graphs and charts in their articles. We therefore developed the <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Chart" class="extiw" title="mw:Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Chart">Charts extension</a>, which will be replacing the old Graph extension and potentially also the <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:EasyTimeline" class="extiw" title="mw:Extension:EasyTimeline">EasyTimeline extension</a>.
</p><p>After successfully deploying the extension on Italian, Swedish, and Hebrew Wikipedia, as well as on MediaWiki.org, as part of a pilot phase, we are now happy to announce that we are moving forward with the next phase of deployment, which will also include your wiki.
</p><p>The deployment will happen in batches, and will start from <b>May 6</b>. Please, consult <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Chart/Project#Deployment_Timeline" class="extiw" title="mw:Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Chart/Project">our page on MediaWiki.org</a> to discover when the new Charts extension will be deployed on your wiki. You can also <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Chart" class="extiw" title="mw:Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Chart">consult the documentation</a> about the extension on MediaWiki.org.
</p><p>If you have questions, need clarifications, or just want to express your opinion about it, please refer to the <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Extension_talk:Chart/Project" class="extiw" title="mw:Special:MyLanguage/Extension talk:Chart/Project">project’s talk page on Mediawiki.org</a>, or ping me directly under this thread. If you encounter issues using Charts once it gets enabled on your wiki, please report it on the <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension_talk:Chart/Project" class="extiw" title="mw:Extension talk:Chart/Project">talk page</a> or at <a href="https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/tag/charts" class="extiw" title="phab:tag/charts">Phabricator</a>.
</p><p>Thank you in advance! -- <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Sannita_(WMF)" title="Uporabnik:Sannita (WMF)">User:Sannita (WMF)</a> (<a href="/w/index.php?title=Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Sannita_(WMF)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Sannita (WMF) (stran ne obstaja)">talk</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">17:08, 6. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250506150800","author":"Sannita (WMF)","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!","replies":["c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800"],"displayName":"User:Sannita (WMF)"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800-We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800"/>Great! — <i><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:GeographieMan" title="Uporabnik:GeographieMan"><b><span style="color: #4863A0;">GeographieMan</span></b></a></i><sup>[<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:GeographieMan" title="Uporabniški pogovor:GeographieMan"><b>~MSG~</b></a>]</sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">20:52, 6. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250506185200","author":"GeographieMan","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-GeographieMan-20250506185200-Sannita_(WMF)-20250506150800"/></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako-20250511044700&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Datum v sklicu javlja napako&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Datum v sklicu javlja napako&quot;}--><h2 id="Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako" data-mw-thread-id="h-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako-20250511044700"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako-20250511044700"/>Datum v sklicu javlja napako<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako-20250511044700"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=36" title="Uredi razdelek: Datum v sklicu javlja napako" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=36" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Datum v sklicu javlja napako"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako-20250511044700","replies":["c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700","timestamp":"20250512100100"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako-20250511044700&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Datum v sklicu javlja napako&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Datum v sklicu javlja napako&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako"/>Pozdravljeni. V <a href="/wiki/Marija_Grafenauer#življenje" class="mw-redirect" title="Marija Grafenauer">Marija Grafenauer#življenje</a> sem v drugi odstavek dodal poimenovan spletni sklic MGML, ki se nanaša na razstravo, pa za polje date= v predogledu javlja napako. Datum je interval (ko je bila razstava odprta), začetni in končni datum sam sta v predogledu sprejeta brez sporočila o napaki, z obema javlja napako. Vezaj sem preizkušal in tudi zahtevani vnešen s priporočeno kodo ‐ (&amp; dash;)  v predogledu še vedno javlja napako. 
</p><p>Prikazan članek ne javlja napake, vendar pa mi bo - če se to v predogledu ne odpravi, težje najti, na katero reč se nanašajo (morebitne, zelo verjetne...) napake pri naslednjih sklicih, ki še pridejo v članek. Lahko kdo, prostim, pojasni, kaj je problem? <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Marjan_Tomki_SI" title="Uporabnik:Marjan Tomki SI">Marjan Tomki SI</a> (<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Marjan_Tomki_SI" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Marjan Tomki SI">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">06:47, 11. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250511044700","author":"Marjan Tomki SI","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako","replies":["c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700-Datum_v_sklicu_javlja_napako"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700"/>Pri virih se navaja datum publikacije. Temu ustrezno sem popravil sklic. lp, --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Smihael" title="Uporabnik:Smihael">Miha</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">12:01, 12. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250512100100","author":"Smihael","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700","replies":[],"displayName":"Miha"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Smihael-20250512100100-Marjan_Tomki_SI-20250511044700"/></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-MARKELLOS-20250512172800&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open-20250512172800&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open&quot;}--><h2 id="Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open" data-mw-thread-id="h-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open-20250512172800"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open-20250512172800"/>Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open-20250512172800"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=37" title="Uredi razdelek: Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=37" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-MARKELLOS-20250512172800","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open-20250512172800","replies":["c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open","timestamp":"20250512172800"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-MARKELLOS-20250512172800&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open-20250512172800&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Registration for the Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025 is open&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open"/>Dear all,              
</p><p>The Organising Committee of the <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025" class="extiw" title="metawiki:Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025">Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025</a> is delighted to announce the opening of the registration for this year's conference.
</p><p>Affiliation and community delegates can register for the meeting until <b>June 15th</b>. All other self-funded participants can register until July 31st.
</p><p>The registration and scholarship application form which runs on Pretix, a free, open-sourced third-party platform that helps organize and manage events, can be found <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pretix.eu/wikimedia-events/wmcee-2025/">here</a>.
</p><p>Details on how to select delegates and the selection process can be found on the <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025/Registration" class="extiw" title="metawiki:Wikimedia CEE Meeting 2025/Registration">registration page</a>.
</p><p>Please keep in mind that the official language of the conference is English and interpreting services will not be available.
</p><p>If you encounter any issues while registering, or have questions about the registration process, feel free to contact the coordination team via <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="mailto:wmceem2025@wikimedia.gr">wmceem2025@wikimedia.gr</a>.
</p><p>Your swift replies will be appreciated, as they will help us conduct an efficient booking process.
</p><p>Best regards,       
</p><p>On behalf of
</p><p><b>Wikimedia CEE M
eeting 2025 Organising Team</b>
</p><p><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:MARKELLOS" title="Uporabnik:MARKELLOS">MARKELLOS</a> (<a href="/w/index.php?title=Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:MARKELLOS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Uporabniški pogovor:MARKELLOS (stran ne obstaja)">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">19:28, 12. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250512172800","author":"MARKELLOS","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-MARKELLOS-20250512172800-Registration_for_the_Wikimedia_CEE_Meeting_2025_is_open"/>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia-20250512200600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia&quot;}--><h2 id="Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia" data-mw-thread-id="h-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia-20250512200600"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia-20250512200600"/>Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia-20250512200600"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=38" title="Uredi razdelek: Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=38" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia-20250512200600","replies":["c-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Smihael-20250513151100-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600","timestamp":"20250513151100"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia-20250512200600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Demographic evolution in table form for populated areas of Slovakia&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia"/>I would like to add: Demographic evolution in table form by places in Slovakia. Anyone against?
</p><p>This is part of a multi-"project" (<a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q132395970" class="extiw" title="wikidata:Q132395970">Modul:SK</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q132395973" class="extiw" title="wikidata:Q132395973">Template:SK</a>). Example of table: <a href="https://hr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fintice#Stanovništvo" class="extiw" title="hr:Fintice">hr:Fintice#Stanovništvo</a>. <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Du%C5%A1an_Krehe%C4%BE" title="Uporabnik:Dušan Kreheľ">Dušan Kreheľ</a> (<a href="/w/index.php?title=Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Du%C5%A1an_Krehe%C4%BE&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Dušan Kreheľ (stran ne obstaja)">pogovor</a>) <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">22:06, 12. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250512200600","author":"Du\u0161an Krehe\u013e","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia","replies":["c-Smihael-20250513151100-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600-Demographic_evolution_in_table_form_for_populated_areas_of_Slovakia"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Smihael-20250513151100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600"/>Primer izgleda v redu in bi bil smiselna dopolnitev obstoječih člankov. Sam bi namesto tabele raje vključil <a href="#We_will_be_enabling_the_new_Charts_extension_on_your_wiki_soon!">graf</a>. lp, --<a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Smihael" title="Uporabnik:Smihael">Miha</a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Smihael-20250513151100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">17:11, 13. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Smihael-20250513151100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250513151100","author":"Smihael","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Smihael-20250513151100-Du\u0161an_Krehe\u013e-20250512200600","replies":[],"displayName":"Miha"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Smihael-20250513151100-Dušan_Kreheľ-20250512200600"/></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Janezdrilc-20250524134300&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko-20250524134300&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Predlog za izbrano sliko&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Predlog za izbrano sliko&quot;}--><h2 id="Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko" data-mw-thread-id="h-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko-20250524134300"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko-20250524134300"/>Predlog za izbrano sliko<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko-20250524134300"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=39" title="Uredi razdelek: Predlog za izbrano sliko" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=39" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Predlog za izbrano sliko"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Janezdrilc-20250524134300","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko-20250524134300","replies":["c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300","timestamp":"20250526041500"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Janezdrilc-20250524134300&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko-20250524134300&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Predlog za izbrano sliko&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Predlog za izbrano sliko&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko"/>Ko je ravno evropski dan parkov ... Razmišljam, da bi dal <a href="/wiki/Slika:Spominski_park_Teharje_2.JPG" title="Slika:Spominski park Teharje 2.JPG">Sliko:Spominski park Teharje 2.JPG</a> za predlog za izbrano sliko, vendar ne vem, ali je možno nominirat sliko, ki prikazuje avtorsko zaščiten objekt. Sliko sem drugače dal v javno last. Prikazan objekt pa je kulturni spomenik državnega pomena Slovenije, zato se mi zdi, da bi tudi na Glavni strani slika pomenila promocijo spomenikov najvišjega ranga v državi.   <span style="letter-spacing: 7px;"><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:Janezdrilc" title="Uporabnik:Janezdrilc"><sup>J</sup><small>a</small><sub>n</sub><small>e</small><sup>z</sup></a><a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:Janezdrilc" title="Uporabniški pogovor:Janezdrilc"><small>d</small><sub>ri</sub><small>l</small><sup>c</sup></a></span> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">15:43, 24. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250524134300","author":"Janezdrilc","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko","replies":["c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300"],"displayName":"Janez"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Janezdrilc-20250524134300-Predlog_za_izbrano_sliko"/>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300"/>Slike pod pošteno uporabo niso za na glavno stran, ker naj bi bile uporabljene v najmanjši možni meri. <a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:MZaplotnik" title="Uporabnik:MZaplotnik"><span style="color:#9370DB;"><strong>MZa</strong></span><span style="color:#8B008B;">plot</span><span style="color:#191970;"><strong>nik</strong></span></a><sup><small>(<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:MZaplotnik" title="Uporabniški pogovor:MZaplotnik">sporočilo</a>)</small></sup> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">06:15, 26. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250526041500","author":"MZaplotnik","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-MZaplotnik-20250526041500-Janezdrilc-20250524134300"/></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-A09-20250527140700&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d-20250527140700&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Uporabni\u0161ke pravice ... drugi\u010d&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Uporabni\u0161ke pravice ... drugi\u010d&quot;}--><h2 id="Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič" data-mw-thread-id="h-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič-20250527140700"><span id="Uporabni.C5.A1ke_pravice_..._drugi.C4.8D"/><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič-20250527140700"/>Uporabniške pravice ... drugič<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič-20250527140700"/></h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=40" title="Uredi razdelek: Uporabniške pravice ... drugič" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>uredi</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedija:Pod_lipo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=40" title="Urejanje izvorne kode razdelka: Uporabniške pravice ... drugič"><span>uredi kodo</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-A09-20250527140700","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d-20250527140700","replies":["c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d","timestamp":"20250527140700"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-A09-20250527140700&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d-20250527140700&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Uporabni\u0161ke pravice ... drugi\u010d&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Uporabni\u0161ke pravice ... drugi\u010d&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič"/>Glede na nedavne spremembe politike vidnosti IP naslovov in predvsem tega, kdo vse bo imel dostop do IP n
aslovov (kot je opisano na <a href="https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Trust_and_Safety_Product/Temporary_Accounts/Updates/2025-05_Access_to_IP_addresses_on_pilot_wikis" class="extiw" title="mw:Trust and Safety Product/Temporary Accounts/Updates/2025-05 Access to IP addresses on pilot wikis">mw:Trust and Safety Product/Temporary Accounts/Updates/2025-05 Access to IP addresses on pilot wikis</a>) bi bilo pametno vzpostaviti vsaj neko osnovno smernico za podeljevanje teh pravic, eno projektno stran, da ne bomo po nepotrebnem obremenjevali WP:PZAB. Ni mi sicer čisto jasno, ali bomo lahko te pravice do vpogleda podeljevali tudi administratorji – slwiki ima namreč očitno neke omejitve pri podeljevanju pravic/jih nima vklopljenih, zato je podeljevanje pravic sedaj bolj stvar birokratov kot pa nas adminov. Kaj menite? Jaz bi še vedno podprl uvedbo dodatnih pravic uporabnikom, kot sem to predlagal že slabe pol leta nazaj. <b><a href="/wiki/Uporabnik:A09" title="Uporabnik:A09"><span style="color:#82201F; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">A09</span></a></b>|<a href="/wiki/Uporabni%C5%A1ki_pogovor:A09" title="Uporabniški pogovor:A09"><span style="color:#797976; text-shadow: 5px 5px 10px #A7A7A3">(pogovor)</span></a> <a href="https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedija:Pod_lipo#c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">16:07, 27. maj 2025 (CEST)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">odgovori</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20250527140700","author":"A09","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabni\u0161ke_pravice_..._drugi\u010d","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-A09-20250527140700-Uporabniške_pravice_..._drugič"/>
</p>
